name: Domojs
body:
### Welcome to DomoJS
The aim of this projet is to create a set of jnode plugins to run on a Raspberry Pi and have a very basic domotic box.

### Authors and Contributors
@npenin

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with DomoJS? contact @npenin or go to [Issues](http://github.com/npenin/domojs/issues).
